Hades/Anubis/Imprisoner/Serpentor/Choran/Predator:



Hades jumped to the right, the quill that had been thrown at him stabbing 
through his left forearm, halfway in, halfway out.  Hades landed, scrambling 
to his feet screaming.

Anubis raised his missile launcher, cursing as he saw Hades get injured.  He 
fired off a rocket at the rock Spears was hiding behind.

===

Predator ducked, the explosion of the missile slamming to the ground hard.  
Raising his grenade launcher, he fired the grenade at the area in between 
Rex's legs, passing out.

Choran yelled, shots digging into him.  He fired off 8 rapid blasts at 
Firearm.

Imprisoner slowly got up, firing a sonic blast at Firearm's left shoulder.

===

Serpentor was slammed backwards from Striker's shots.  He cursed, his plasma 
launcher appearing in his left hand from subspace, firing a blast off at 
Striker's left shoulder.
